channel.title: [PI] Dark-Spirits V1
channel.description:
[IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/2ldv9yw.png[/img]
[b]Introduction:[/b]
Hello everyone, So i decided to release my work, after a period of time not using it, Well it's my first release, I hope you guys enjoy this :)
[b]Features:[/b]
[code] NPC Clipling full working Perfect switching Single doors fully working Npc Hp bar (HP Bar refilling) Trading in shoutbox (wishs to trade with you) New quest tab Fix Client background crashing Ladder system Fix for some models ALL skills has been edited (Including new animations & gfx) New Pk shop & more new shops All other shops has been edited All npc spawn has been edited (Including more training areas) All dialogues has been edited New pest control New combat levels system Hunter & summon bugfix EP system has been removed Chat logs PM logs Re-coded commands.java Including: (New commands with interfaces for all ranks) New Graphics New skillcapes system Skill tab interfaces New moderators island Dupe fix -I've added more which i can't even remember :) [/code]
